fields.name: ExcludedPatchCount
fields.description: The number of all available patches but excluded explicitly by a customer-specified exclusion list match.

fields.name: FailedPatchCount
fields.description: The count of patches that failed installation.

fields.name: InstallationActivityId
fields.description: The activity ID of the operation that produced this result. It is used to correlate across CRP and extension logs.

fields.name: InstalledPatchCount
fields.description: The count of patches that successfully installed.

fields.name: LastModifiedTime
fields.description: The UTC timestamp when the operation began.

fields.name: MaintenanceWindowExceeded
fields.description: Describes whether the operation ran out of time before it completed all its intended actions

fields.name: NotSelectedPatchCount
fields.description: The number of all available patches but not going to be installed because it didn't match a classification or inclusion list entry.

fields.name: PendingPatchCount
fields.description: The number of all available patches expected to be installed over the course of the patch installation operation.

fields.name: StartTime
fields.description: The UTC timestamp when the operation began.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The overall success or failure status of the operation. It remains "InProgress" until the operation completes. At that point it will become "Unknown", "Failed", "Succeeded", or "CompletedWithWarnings."
